metadata.name: The Whisperer
metadata.description:
His words are like the touch of sunlight on your skin, warm and soothing. 

-----

This piece was created using an iterative back-and-forth process capturing and curating raw digitographs using very specific prompt engineering techniques on custom and pre-trained (Stable Diffusion) AI models.

It was further refined using Photoshop to experiment with colors and aesthetics in order to accentuate or reveal the stylistic aspects of the main subject I have chosen.
